1
00:00:09,109 --> 00:00:12,345
Speedwagon: JOJO WON HIS BATTLE
AGAINST THAT DEMON.

2
00:00:12,412 --> 00:00:13,580
POOR SOD.

3
00:00:13,647 --> 00:00:15,582
HE LOST EVERYTHING
IN THE PROCESS.

4
00:00:15,649 --> 00:00:18,519
THAT'S WHY I BROUGHT HIM HERE
THREE DAYS AGO.

5
00:00:18,619 --> 00:00:21,087
AND NOW, BEREFT OF FATHER
AND HOME ALIKE,

6
00:00:21,154 --> 00:00:24,290
HOW'S HE GONNA MUSTER UP
THE WILL TO LIVE?

7
00:00:24,357 --> 00:00:27,093
DON'T GIVE UP
ON THE WORLD YET, JOJO!

8
00:00:27,160 --> 00:00:29,362
♪

9
00:00:36,436 --> 00:00:38,539
( singing in Japanese )

10
00:01:59,593 --> 00:02:01,467
( cane tapping )

11
00:02:01,535 --> 00:02:02,536
SPIRIT...

12
00:02:02,603 --> 00:02:04,270
THAT'S WHAT HE NEEDS,

13
00:02:04,304 --> 00:02:06,406
SO I'M GONNA GIVE IT TO HIM.

14
00:02:06,472 --> 00:02:07,407
HUH?

15
00:02:07,473 --> 00:02:09,442
IT'S THE DEAD OF NIGHT,

16
00:02:09,475 --> 00:02:12,212
BUT THERE'S A LAMP BURNING
IN HIS ROOM.

17
00:02:12,278 --> 00:02:14,881
♪

18
00:02:16,049 --> 00:02:17,717
WHAT DO WE HAVE HERE?

19
00:02:22,288 --> 00:02:24,057
HOW LONG'S SHE BEEN AT IT?

20
00:02:24,124 --> 00:02:27,994
DON'T TELL ME SHE'S BEEN
WATCHING OVER HIM ALL THIS TIME.

21
00:02:28,061 --> 00:02:29,896
( gasps ) HER FINGERS,

22
00:02:29,963 --> 00:02:31,898
CRACKED FROM THE DAMP,
I'D WAGER.

23
00:02:31,965 --> 00:02:34,267
SHE MUST HAVE BEEN COOLING
HIS BURNS ROUND THE CLOCK

24
00:02:34,334 --> 00:02:36,937
FOR THEM TO GET LIKE THAT LIKE.

25
00:02:37,003 --> 00:02:38,772
‐ ( JoJo sighs )
‐ ( Erina gasps )

26
00:02:49,282 --> 00:02:50,651
THANK GOODNESS.

27
00:02:50,684 --> 00:02:52,418
( Speedwagon gasps )
HE'S AWAKE.

28
00:02:52,485 --> 00:02:54,521
Erina: YOU'RE THROUGH
THE WORST OF IT.

29
00:02:54,621 --> 00:02:55,922
YOU SHOULD BE FINE.

30
00:02:55,989 --> 00:02:59,025
JoJo: SO YOU'VE BEEN
TENDING TO MY INJURIES?

31
00:02:59,092 --> 00:03:03,537
BUT HOW CAN‐‐HOW CAN
YOU BE STANDING HERE?

32
00:03:03,637 --> 00:03:06,106
YOU'RE THE IMAGE OF‐‐

33
00:03:06,172 --> 00:03:09,009
BUT NO. I'M SORRY.

34
00:03:09,042 --> 00:03:13,446
YOUR FACE REMINDS ME
OF A GIRL I USED TO KNOW.

35
00:03:13,514 --> 00:03:17,483
HER NAME WOULDN'T HAPPEN TO BE
ERINA PENDLETON, WOULD IT?

36
00:03:17,551 --> 00:03:19,285
JoJo: IT'S YOU.

37
00:03:19,352 --> 00:03:22,789
Erina: IT'S BEEN A LONG TIME,
JONATHAN JOESTAR...

38
00:03:22,856 --> 00:03:23,790
JOJO.

39
00:03:23,857 --> 00:03:26,026
JoJo: ERINA,
YOU'VE REALLY GROWN UP.

40
00:03:26,059 --> 00:03:29,830
Erina: ME? BUT YOU'VE GROWN
A FAIR SIGHT MORE.

41
00:03:31,164 --> 00:03:32,633
YET...

42
00:03:32,699 --> 00:03:36,803
YOU'RE STILL THE BOY YOU WERE.

43
00:03:37,671 --> 00:03:38,805
JoJo: YEAH.

44
00:03:43,076 --> 00:03:45,712
Speedwagon: SHE MAKES
A BETTER FLORENCE NIGHTINGALE

45
00:03:45,746 --> 00:03:47,213
THAN I DO ANYHOW.

46
00:03:47,247 --> 00:03:50,416
YOU REST UP, JOJO.

47
00:03:50,517 --> 00:03:53,419
TIME FOR SPEEDWAGON
TO MAKE HIS EXIT.

48
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:55,055
( Erina gasps )

49
00:03:58,224 --> 00:04:01,535
I‐‐I MUST HAVE FAINTED
FOR A MOMENT.

50
00:04:01,602 --> 00:04:03,336
( gasps ) BUT YOUR ARM,

51
00:04:03,403 --> 00:04:05,772
IT'S BROKEN.
YOU SHOULDN'T HAVE CAUGHT ME.

52
00:04:05,872 --> 00:04:07,440
( JoJo chuckles )

53
00:04:07,508 --> 00:04:09,743
YOU CAUGHT ME LONG AGO.

54
00:04:10,877 --> 00:04:12,345
Speedwagon:
I DARESAY OL' JOJO

55
00:04:12,412 --> 00:04:16,049
WON'T BE LACKING A REASON
TO LIVE AFTER THIS REUNION.

56
00:04:16,116 --> 00:04:18,084
♪

57
00:04:19,285 --> 00:04:21,888
Man: YOU SHOULD HAVE MADE
AN EARLY NIGHT OF IT,

58
00:04:21,955 --> 00:04:23,289
YOU HARLOT. BIG MISTAKE.

59
00:04:23,356 --> 00:04:24,290
( woman screams )

60
00:04:24,357 --> 00:04:26,960
( Jack laughs )

61
00:04:27,027 --> 00:04:30,196
Dio: MOST MEN SHACKLE THEMSELVES
TO PETTY MORALITY.

62
00:04:30,263 --> 00:04:31,297
Jack: HUH?

63
00:04:31,364 --> 00:04:34,033
Dio: THEY FEAR
THE CONSEQUENCES OF THEIR EVIL.

64
00:04:34,100 --> 00:04:35,969
‐ ( apothecary laughs )
‐ Dio: BUT SOME ARE UNFETTERED

65
00:04:36,035 --> 00:04:38,605
BY MAN'S LAWS
IN ALL THEIR TYRANNY.

66
00:04:38,638 --> 00:04:40,040
THEY ARE THE VANGUARD.

67
00:04:40,106 --> 00:04:43,109
BECOME MY SERVANT,
JACK THE RIPPER.

68
00:04:43,143 --> 00:04:45,579
YOU'VE NO FURTHER NEED
FOR FREE WILL.

69
00:04:45,646 --> 00:04:47,814
( Jack groans )

70
00:04:47,914 --> 00:04:50,150
Dio: I WILL MAKE YOU
AN INSTRUMENT OF DEATH

71
00:04:50,216 --> 00:04:52,619
THE LIKES OF WHICH
YOU CAN'T BEGIN TO IMAGINE.

72
00:04:52,653 --> 00:04:53,820
Jack: DO IT.

73
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:56,990
Dio: AS FOR WHAT
I SHALL TAKE IN RETURN...

74
00:04:59,125 --> 00:05:01,067
( squelching )

75
00:05:04,671 --> 00:05:06,807
JoJo: ONLY SPEEDWAGON AND I

76
00:05:06,840 --> 00:05:09,643
KNOW WHAT TRULY
TOOK PLACE HERE THAT NIGHT.

77
00:05:09,676 --> 00:05:12,746
DIO WAS CONSUMED IN THE INFERNO,

78
00:05:12,813 --> 00:05:14,815
BUT WHAT OF THE ACCURSED MASK?

79
00:05:14,848 --> 00:05:17,350
NO SIGN OF IT IN THE RUBBLE.

80
00:05:17,450 --> 00:05:20,153
SMASHED BY FALLING MASONRY?

81
00:05:20,186 --> 00:05:24,124
I HOPE SO. I WANT TO PUT
THIS NIGHTMARE BEHIND ME.

82
00:05:24,190 --> 00:05:25,191
Erina: JOJO.

83
00:05:26,426 --> 00:05:27,794
JoJo: ERINA.

84
00:05:37,203 --> 00:05:38,304
HMM?

85
00:05:40,173 --> 00:05:43,944
THAT MAN, HE HAUNTS OUR STEPS.

86
00:05:44,010 --> 00:05:45,378
Erina: IS SOMETHING WRONG?

87
00:05:45,478 --> 00:05:47,147
JoJo: NO. ALL IS WELL.

88
00:05:47,213 --> 00:05:48,148
( gasps )

89
00:05:48,214 --> 00:05:49,983
♪

90
00:05:53,486 --> 00:05:54,788
( gasps )

91
00:05:54,855 --> 00:05:57,457
Man: AH, SIGNORE JOESTAR.

92
00:05:57,524 --> 00:06:01,535
AND THE LASS AT YOUR SIDE
IS SIGNORINA PENDLETON.

93
00:06:01,568 --> 00:06:02,569
( man grunts )

94
00:06:02,669 --> 00:06:04,237
( JoJo gasps )
WHO ARE YOU?!

95
00:06:04,304 --> 00:06:06,472
Man: YOU SURVIVED
AGAINST THE MASK.

96
00:06:06,540 --> 00:06:08,174
NOT MANY MEN CAN CLAIM THAT.

97
00:06:08,241 --> 00:06:10,043
‐ ( JoJo gasps )
‐ ( man yells )

98
00:06:11,745 --> 00:06:13,647
‐ ( JoJo yelps )
‐ Erina: JOJO!

99
00:06:13,714 --> 00:06:15,081
( JoJo gasping )

100
00:06:15,148 --> 00:06:16,917
‐ ( coughs )
‐ Man: THAT'S RIGHT.

101
00:06:17,017 --> 00:06:20,053
LET THE SHOCK OF THAT IMPACT
PUSH ALL THE AIR FROM YOUR BODY.

102
00:06:20,086 --> 00:06:23,389
‐ ( JoJo gasps )
‐ Erina: JOJO! WHY?

103
00:06:23,423 --> 00:06:25,191
HE WAS ALREADY HURT, YOU CAD!

104
00:06:25,258 --> 00:06:28,562
Man: IT'S TRUE
I KNOCKED THE AIR OUT OF HIM,

105
00:06:28,595 --> 00:06:30,196
BUT HE'LL THANK ME FOR IT.

106
00:06:30,263 --> 00:06:32,398
‐ ( JoJo gasps )
‐ ( bones cracking )

107
00:06:32,432 --> 00:06:33,399
MY ARM!

108
00:06:35,001 --> 00:06:38,772
WHAT IS THIS? MY BROKEN BONES...

109
00:06:38,872 --> 00:06:40,741
FEEL LIKE THEY'RE MENDING!

110
00:06:40,774 --> 00:06:43,076
Zeppeli: BARON ZEPPELI,
AT YOUR SERVICE.

111
00:06:43,109 --> 00:06:46,346
COURAGE ALONE WILL NOT BE
ENOUGH TO BEAT THE MASK.

112
00:06:46,412 --> 00:06:49,516
JoJo: MY ARM WAS SHATTERED,
BUT NOW...

113
00:06:51,552 --> 00:06:53,186
THE PAIN HAS SUBSIDED.

114
00:06:53,253 --> 00:06:55,756
LIFTING THIS ROCK IS NOTHING.

115
00:06:55,789 --> 00:06:57,558
Erina: THAT'S INCREDIBLE.

116
00:06:57,624 --> 00:06:59,893
JoJo: SIR, WHY ARE YOU HERE?

117
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:01,768
AND WHAT IS HAPPENING TO ME?

118
00:07:01,802 --> 00:07:03,570
Zeppeli: PLEASE,
TRY TO LIMIT YOURSELF

119
00:07:03,637 --> 00:07:06,139
TO ONE QUESTION AT A TIME.

120
00:07:06,206 --> 00:07:07,908
YOU HEALED YOURSELF, JOJO.

121
00:07:07,974 --> 00:07:11,244
HOW YOU BREATHED
AFTER I POKED YOU WAS THE KEY.

122
00:07:12,412 --> 00:07:15,048
( sneezes )

123
00:07:16,650 --> 00:07:19,986
JoJo: BUT WHY DID YOU GO TO
THE TROUBLE IN THE FIRST PLACE?

124
00:07:20,086 --> 00:07:22,455
AND HOW DO YOU KNOW
WHO I‐‐HE'S GONE.

125
00:07:22,488 --> 00:07:26,627
Zeppeli: WHAT PART OF "ONE
QUESTION AT A TIME" ELUDED YOU?

126
00:07:26,660 --> 00:07:30,130
YOU'LL GET THE ANSWERS
YOU DESIRE, AMICO. FOLLOW ME.

127
00:07:30,163 --> 00:07:32,498
THIS DAY, I WILL SHOW YOU THINGS

128
00:07:32,566 --> 00:07:36,436
THE LIKES OF WHICH WILL CHANGE
YOUR DESTINY FOREVER.

129
00:07:36,503 --> 00:07:38,839
( JoJo gasps )

130
00:07:39,940 --> 00:07:41,341
Zeppeli: IT WAS WITH GOOD REASON

131
00:07:41,407 --> 00:07:43,243
THAT I STRUCK YOU
IN THE DIAPHRAGM.

132
00:07:43,309 --> 00:07:46,346
THE SHOCK OF THE IMPACT
ALTERED YOUR BREATHING.

133
00:07:46,446 --> 00:07:48,582
JoJo: BUT HOW DID THAT
HEAL MY ARM?

134
00:07:48,649 --> 00:07:51,818
Zeppeli: WITH THE ENERGY I AM
ABOUT TO DEMONSTRATE FOR YOU.

135
00:07:51,852 --> 00:07:53,419
♪

136
00:07:53,486 --> 00:07:56,189
JoJo: WAIT.
WHAT MISCHIEF IS HE PLANNING?

137
00:07:56,289 --> 00:07:58,458
( Zeppeli breathing deeply )

138
00:08:02,302 --> 00:08:04,370
( grunting )

139
00:08:06,306 --> 00:08:08,208
( yelling )

140
00:08:12,112 --> 00:08:13,614
JoJo: LOOK AT HIM, ERINA.

141
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:16,850
HIS LEGS. THOSE RIPPLES.

142
00:08:16,883 --> 00:08:19,052
I'VE NEVER SEEN WATER DO THAT.

143
00:08:19,119 --> 00:08:21,888
Zeppeli: WHAT YOU SEE IS
THE FORCE THAT EASED YOUR PAIN

144
00:08:21,988 --> 00:08:23,724
AND HEALED YOUR BROKEN BONES,
SIGNORE JOESTAR.

145
00:08:23,824 --> 00:08:26,192
( yells )

146
00:08:26,226 --> 00:08:28,228
‐ JoJo: DON'T DO IT!
‐ ( Erina screams )

147
00:08:30,697 --> 00:08:31,632
( Zeppeli chuckles )

148
00:08:32,733 --> 00:08:35,035
( yells )

149
00:08:36,136 --> 00:08:38,805
( frog croaking )

150
00:08:38,872 --> 00:08:39,806
( JoJo gasps )

151
00:08:39,873 --> 00:08:41,808
THAT FROG SEEMS NONE THE WORSE.

152
00:08:41,875 --> 00:08:44,545
Zeppeli: THAT WAS SENDO YOU SAW.

153
00:08:44,578 --> 00:08:45,912
JoJo: WAIT. "SENDO"?

154
00:08:46,012 --> 00:08:49,215
Zeppeli: IT'S RIPPLE ENERGY
CREATED BY HAMON.

155
00:08:49,249 --> 00:08:52,218
I SENT MY HAMON COURSING
HARMLESSLY THROUGH FROGGY

156
00:08:52,252 --> 00:08:55,355
TO SPLIT MY REAL TARGET,
THE ROCK BELOW.

157
00:08:56,256 --> 00:08:58,925
JOJO, I KNOW FOR A FACT

158
00:08:59,025 --> 00:09:01,101
THE STONE MASK
WAS NOT DESTROYED.

159
00:09:01,167 --> 00:09:04,104
DIO BRANDO KEEPS IT
CLOSE TO HIM EVEN NOW.

160
00:09:04,170 --> 00:09:05,872
JoJo: NO, IT CAN'T BE.

161
00:09:05,939 --> 00:09:08,008
BARON, IS DIO STILL ALIVE?

162
00:09:08,074 --> 00:09:10,611
Zeppeli: INDEED,
AND HE HOLDS THE MASK

163
00:09:10,711 --> 00:09:12,779
I HAVE SOUGHT FOR DECADES NOW.

164
00:09:12,879 --> 00:09:15,115
THAT MASK MUST BE DESTROYED,

165
00:09:15,215 --> 00:09:17,784
AND ITS MASTER
MUST BE REDUCED TO ASH.

166
00:09:17,851 --> 00:09:21,555
IT IS YOUR DESTINY TO FIGHT
FOR THIS RIGHTEOUS CAUSE.

167
00:09:21,622 --> 00:09:25,291
YOU WILL LEARN TO WIELD SENDO,
OR YOU WILL DIE.

168
00:09:25,391 --> 00:09:27,794
THE FUTURE OF HUMANITY
IS AT STAKE!

169
00:09:27,894 --> 00:09:29,229
JoJo: MY DESTINY?

170
00:09:29,295 --> 00:09:31,231
Erina: WHAT IS HE TALKING ABOUT?

171
00:09:31,297 --> 00:09:33,433
NONE OF IT MAKES ANY SENSE.

172
00:09:33,466 --> 00:09:34,234
( JoJo gasps )

173
00:09:34,300 --> 00:09:36,603
( thinking )
ERINA.

174
00:09:36,637 --> 00:09:39,239
SHE'S ALREADY SUFFERED
ENOUGH AT DIO'S HANDS.

175
00:09:39,305 --> 00:09:41,441
I CAN'T DRAG HER INTO THIS.

176
00:09:42,909 --> 00:09:43,810
( Zeppeli gasps )

177
00:09:43,910 --> 00:09:46,112
INCREDIBLE.

178
00:09:46,146 --> 00:09:47,648
IT'S BLOSSOMING!

179
00:09:47,714 --> 00:09:50,450
HE'S PASSING THE SPARE
HAMON ENERGY FROM HIS HEALED ARM

180
00:09:50,483 --> 00:09:52,619
INTO THE BRANCH
AND SENDING IT INTO BLOOM.

181
00:09:52,653 --> 00:09:56,623
AND AMAZINGLY HE DOESN'T
EVEN REALIZE HE'S DOING IT.

182
00:09:56,657 --> 00:09:58,625
THIS BOY, HE IS A NATURAL.

183
00:09:58,659 --> 00:10:00,426
OF WHAT MIGHT HE BE CAPABLE,

184
00:10:00,493 --> 00:10:03,103
WITH THE PROPER REFINEMENT
OF HIS ABILITIES?

185
00:10:03,203 --> 00:10:04,771
REJOICE, MANKIND.

186
00:10:04,871 --> 00:10:07,541
THIS DAY, I MAY HAVE FOUND
YOUR CHAMPION.

187
00:10:10,443 --> 00:10:12,445
( woman screams )

188
00:10:12,513 --> 00:10:13,446
( body falls )

189
00:10:13,514 --> 00:10:15,248
♪

190
00:10:15,281 --> 00:10:16,950
Dio: MMM.

191
00:10:17,017 --> 00:10:20,887
WITH EVERY MEAL,
I FEEL MY STRENGTH RETURNING.

192
00:10:20,954 --> 00:10:23,690
WHAT A SIMPLE THING,
THE FOOD CHAIN.

193
00:10:23,757 --> 00:10:27,460
AS PIGS FEED ON GRASS,
SO DOES MAN FEED UPON THEM,

194
00:10:27,561 --> 00:10:31,264
AND I, AT THE TOP OF IT ALL,
FEED UPON THE HUMANS.

195
00:10:31,297 --> 00:10:35,702
THEY EXIST TO SERVE ME
AND QUELL MY THIRST.

196
00:10:35,769 --> 00:10:38,471
GO, JACK. IT'S SUPPERTIME.

197
00:10:38,539 --> 00:10:40,306
( Jack growls )

198
00:10:40,373 --> 00:10:43,777
Dio: NOW TO SWELL THE RANKS
OF MY DIABOLICAL ARMY

199
00:10:43,810 --> 00:10:45,378
AND SEND IT HENCE.

200
00:10:45,445 --> 00:10:47,981
I WILL STAND ASTRIDE THIS WORLD.

201
00:10:48,048 --> 00:10:51,652
HUMANITY WILL KNEEL
AT DIO BRANDO'S FEET.

202
00:10:54,788 --> 00:10:56,389
♪

203
00:10:56,456 --> 00:10:58,491
JoJo: AND SO I BEGAN
TO STUDY HAMON

204
00:10:58,559 --> 00:11:01,067
UNDER THE TUTELAGE
OF THE MYSTERIOUS ZEPPELI.

205
00:11:01,134 --> 00:11:05,305
THE TRAINING WAS SPARTAN,
BUT I HAD NO CHOICE.

206
00:11:05,338 --> 00:11:07,974
HERE'S HOW IT CAME ABOUT.

207
00:11:08,008 --> 00:11:10,944
Zeppeli: JOJO, MY HISTORY
WITH THE STONE MASK

208
00:11:11,011 --> 00:11:12,646
HAS BEEN A LONG ONE.

209
00:11:12,679 --> 00:11:14,615
I WAS YOUR AGE.

210
00:11:14,681 --> 00:11:17,618
HARD TO BELIEVE
THAT WAS EVER THE CASE NOW.

211
00:11:17,684 --> 00:11:20,086
I HARBORED A GREAT THIRST
FOR ADVENTURE,

212
00:11:20,153 --> 00:11:22,188
AS THE YOUNG SO OFTEN DO.

213
00:11:22,255 --> 00:11:25,191
IT WAS MY GOOD FORTUNE
TO TRAVEL THE WORLD

214
00:11:25,258 --> 00:11:28,161
AS A MEMBER OF MY FATHER'S
ARCHAEOLOGICAL TEAM.

215
00:11:28,194 --> 00:11:30,430
WOULD THAT WE
HAD NEVER LAIN EYES

216
00:11:30,496 --> 00:11:32,633
ON THOSE AZTEC RUINS THAT DAY.

217
00:11:32,699 --> 00:11:33,867
JoJo: YOU'RE SAYING...

218
00:11:33,934 --> 00:11:35,035
Zeppeli: YES.

219
00:11:35,135 --> 00:11:37,303
THE HANDS THAT PULLED
THAT EVIL ARTIFACT

220
00:11:37,370 --> 00:11:40,340
INTO THE LIGHT OF DAY
BELONGED TO ME.

221
00:11:40,373 --> 00:11:43,710
ONE ILL‐FATED NIGHT
DURING THE VOYAGE HOME,

222
00:11:43,810 --> 00:11:46,947
A MAN OF OUR NUMBER
SUCCUMBED TO HIS CURIOSITY

223
00:11:47,013 --> 00:11:49,349
AND DONNED THE MASK.

224
00:11:49,382 --> 00:11:51,552
‐ ( thunder crashes )
‐ ( man screams )

225
00:11:51,618 --> 00:11:54,020
Zeppeli: THE CHANGE IN HIM
WAS IMMEDIATE.

226
00:11:54,054 --> 00:11:55,455
RAMPAGING THROUGH THE SHIP,

227
00:11:55,522 --> 00:11:57,724
HE RIPPED
HIS COMPANIONS' HEADS OFF

228
00:11:57,791 --> 00:11:59,560
IN A BACCHANALIA OF BLOOD.

229
00:11:59,626 --> 00:12:03,570
58 CREWMEN BUTCHERED
IN A MATTER OF MINUTES.

230
00:12:03,637 --> 00:12:08,208
I DOVE INTO THE SEA TO ESCAPE,
BUT THE FIEND GAVE CHASE.

231
00:12:08,241 --> 00:12:10,911
( creature roars )

232
00:12:10,977 --> 00:12:12,078
( Zeppeli gasps )

233
00:12:12,178 --> 00:12:14,748
SUDDENLY DAWN BROKE.

234
00:12:16,216 --> 00:12:18,752
AS HE CRUMBLED TO DUST
IN THE SUNLIGHT,

235
00:12:18,852 --> 00:12:20,754
I SAW HIS FACE...

236
00:12:24,224 --> 00:12:27,060
AND TO MY UTTER HORROR,

237
00:12:27,093 --> 00:12:29,596
THE DEMON WAS MY FATHER.

238
00:12:29,663 --> 00:12:34,200
THE CREWLESS SHIP DRIFTED AWAY
WITH THE MASK STILL ABOARD.

239
00:12:34,267 --> 00:12:37,103
I HAD SURVIVED,
BUT IT WAS COLD COMFORT,

240
00:12:37,203 --> 00:12:40,907
KNOWING THE MASK'S DREADFUL
POWER COULD BE UNLEASHED AGAIN.

241
00:12:40,941 --> 00:12:45,111
I DEDICATED MY LIFE TO FINDING
A WAY TO STOP ITS EVIL.

242
00:12:45,178 --> 00:12:48,281
THAT PLEDGE LED
TO MY DISCOVERY OF HAMON.

243
00:12:48,348 --> 00:12:50,350
THE ENERGY WE CALL HAMON

244
00:12:50,416 --> 00:12:53,086
IS CREATED BY THE FLOW
OF ONE'S BLOOD.

245
00:12:53,119 --> 00:12:54,621
THOSE WHO WEAR THE MASK

246
00:12:54,688 --> 00:12:57,891
FEED ON THE BLOOD OF OTHERS
TO CONSUME THAT ENERGY.

247
00:12:57,958 --> 00:13:01,735
HAMON AND THE MASK, THEY ARE
TWO SIDES OF THE SAME COIN.

248
00:13:01,802 --> 00:13:02,903
JoJo: OF COURSE.

249
00:13:02,969 --> 00:13:05,872
WE CAN OVERLOAD DIO
WITH THAT WHICH ANIMATES HIM.

250
00:13:05,939 --> 00:13:09,543
Zeppeli: CORRECT. IF WE CAN HIT
DIO WITH ENOUGH HAMON ENERGY,

251
00:13:09,610 --> 00:13:11,144
THAT DEVIL WILL BURST ASUNDER.

252
00:13:11,244 --> 00:13:13,213
HAMON'S RIPPLES
ARE THE SAME FORM

253
00:13:13,279 --> 00:13:16,750
AS THE WAVES OF LIGHT
SENT OUT BY THE SUN ITSELF,

254
00:13:16,817 --> 00:13:18,484
THE BANE OF ALL VAMPIRES.

255
00:13:20,086 --> 00:13:22,288
JoJo: BARON ZEPPELI,
I BEG OF YOU,

256
00:13:22,322 --> 00:13:24,290
TEACH ME HOW TO WIELD IT.

257
00:13:24,324 --> 00:13:26,459
I PROMISE I'LL GIVE IT MY ALL.

258
00:13:26,492 --> 00:13:29,663
Zeppeli: YOU DON'T GET A CHOICE
IN THE MATTER, AMICO.

259
00:13:29,763 --> 00:13:31,732
GIVEN YOUR CONTENTIOUS HISTORY
WITH DIO,

260
00:13:31,798 --> 00:13:34,668
I'M SURE
HE WILL BE COMING FOR YOU.

261
00:13:34,735 --> 00:13:37,838
( laughs )

262
00:13:37,938 --> 00:13:39,239
♪

263
00:13:39,305 --> 00:13:41,608
THERE IS A POETRY TO THIS, JOJO.

264
00:13:41,675 --> 00:13:44,277
BREATHING OXYGENATES YOUR BLOOD.

265
00:13:44,344 --> 00:13:47,147
YOUR BLOOD CARRIES THE OXYGEN
THROUGHOUT YOUR BODY.

266
00:13:47,180 --> 00:13:48,348
IT ENRICHES THE CELLS,

267
00:13:48,448 --> 00:13:51,117
GIVING THEM
THE POWER TO KEEP ON LIVING.

268
00:13:51,184 --> 00:13:53,153
THOSE CELLS COMBINE TO FORM YOU.

269
00:13:53,186 --> 00:13:54,988
LIKE RIPPLES IN THE WATER,

270
00:13:55,021 --> 00:13:58,491
YOUR BODY THRUMS WITH THE HAMON
CREATED BY PROPER BREATHING.

271
00:13:58,525 --> 00:14:00,834
ALL THAT IS LEFT IS TO USE IT!

272
00:14:00,867 --> 00:14:02,335
( JoJo grunts )

273
00:14:02,368 --> 00:14:04,337
THERE'S NO WAY HE COULD HAVE
REACHED ME FROM THERE.

274
00:14:04,370 --> 00:14:06,707
HOW DID HE DO THAT?

275
00:14:06,773 --> 00:14:09,175
Zeppeli: ZOOM PUNCH
IS A USEFUL ONE.

276
00:14:09,209 --> 00:14:10,877
I MERELY DISLOCATED MY SHOULDER.

277
00:14:10,977 --> 00:14:12,178
HAMON DULLS THE PAIN,

278
00:14:12,212 --> 00:14:14,715
AND THE SURPRISE
IS WELL WORTH THE EFFORT.

279
00:14:14,781 --> 00:14:17,383
YOU MUST MAINTAIN
THE RHYTHM OF YOUR BREATH,

280
00:14:17,450 --> 00:14:19,052
EVEN WHEN TAKING A HIT.

281
00:14:19,119 --> 00:14:21,221
IF YOUR MIND OR HEART
ARE TEMPESTUOUS,

282
00:14:21,321 --> 00:14:23,389
THE CALIBER OF YOUR HAMON
WILL SUFFER.

283
00:14:23,456 --> 00:14:24,891
‐ JoJo: YES, SIR.
‐ Speedwagon: OI!

284
00:14:24,991 --> 00:14:26,292
I FOUND SOMETHING!

285
00:14:26,359 --> 00:14:28,529
JoJo: EH? SPEEDWAGON.

286
00:14:28,562 --> 00:14:31,532
SO THE VILLAGE
IS CALLED WIND KNIGHTS LOT?

287
00:14:31,565 --> 00:14:33,534
Speedwagon: RIGHT.
THEY'VE HAD A STRING

288
00:14:33,567 --> 00:14:35,802
OF DISAPPEARANCES LATELY,
PEOPLE VANISHING AFTER DARK,

289
00:14:35,869 --> 00:14:39,640
AND FOLKS HAVE CAUGHT GLIMPSES
OF A FELLA WHO LOOKS LIKE DIO.

290
00:14:39,706 --> 00:14:41,141
Zeppeli: WE'RE OUT OF TIME NOW.

291
00:14:41,207 --> 00:14:44,144
YOUR FINAL TEST WILL BE ONE
OF LIFE OR DEATH, MY PUPIL.

292
00:14:44,210 --> 00:14:47,514
JoJo: YES, SIR. I'LL MEET HIM
IN COMBAT AND LAY HIM LOW.

293
00:14:47,581 --> 00:14:49,249
Speedwagon: GIVE HIM HELL.

294
00:14:49,315 --> 00:14:50,684
LOOK, GENTS.

295
00:14:50,751 --> 00:14:52,886
THE ENTRANCE
TO WIND KNIGHTS LOT.

296
00:14:52,919 --> 00:14:54,154
JoJo: WE'LL ATTACK DIO

297
00:14:54,220 --> 00:14:56,757
WHILE THERE'S STILL PLENTY
OF LIGHT LEFT IN THE SKY.

298
00:14:56,823 --> 00:15:00,426
♪

299
00:15:00,527 --> 00:15:05,906
ERINA. I LEFT WITHOUT
GIVING YOU A PROPER FAREWELL.

300
00:15:05,939 --> 00:15:08,675
I SWEAR I WILL RETURN TO HER.

301
00:15:12,345 --> 00:15:13,847
( thump )

302
00:15:13,914 --> 00:15:14,848
Speedwagon: HUH?

303
00:15:16,883 --> 00:15:17,784
JoJo: WHY DID WE STOP?

304
00:15:17,851 --> 00:15:20,787
Speedwagon: OI, MATE!
HURRY IT UP!

305
00:15:20,887 --> 00:15:21,855
JoJo: KEEP AN EYE OUT.

306
00:15:21,922 --> 00:15:23,624
SUNLIGHT CAN'T PROTECT US
IN HERE.

307
00:15:23,690 --> 00:15:25,526
Zeppeli: WELL? WHAT'S WRONG?

308
00:15:25,592 --> 00:15:27,794
( Speedwagon gasps )

309
00:15:27,861 --> 00:15:30,797
( screams )

310
00:15:30,897 --> 00:15:32,966
♪

311
00:15:35,068 --> 00:15:36,803
JoJo: IS IT DIO?

312
00:15:36,903 --> 00:15:38,539
IT HAS TO BE HIM.

313
00:15:38,605 --> 00:15:40,140
Zeppeli: LISTEN, BOTH OF YOU.

314
00:15:40,206 --> 00:15:42,475
STEP AWAY FROM THE HORSES.

315
00:15:42,576 --> 00:15:45,411
( Jack growling )

316
00:15:47,447 --> 00:15:49,616
( Speedwagon gasps )
WHAT IN THE BLUE HELL?!

317
00:15:49,650 --> 00:15:51,752
THAT CRAZY BLIGHTER'S
INSIDE OUR HORSE!

318
00:15:53,319 --> 00:15:56,289
GOOD GOD,
THIS ONE'S MAD AS A HATTER!

319
00:15:56,322 --> 00:15:57,758
DIO'S EVIL, YEAH,

320
00:15:57,824 --> 00:16:00,801
BUT I AIN'T SEEN HIM
JUMP OUT OF ANY ANIMALS SO FAR.

321
00:16:00,834 --> 00:16:02,168
JoJo: HE MUST BE
GATHERING MINIONS,

322
00:16:02,268 --> 00:16:03,970
AND WHO KNOWS
HOW MANY HE MIGHT HAVE?

323
00:16:05,506 --> 00:16:08,509
( Zeppeli sighs )
STAND ASIDE, MY YOUNG FRIENDS.

324
00:16:08,575 --> 00:16:10,243
I WILL DO THE FIGHTING.

325
00:16:10,310 --> 00:16:11,612
( Jack growls )

326
00:16:11,678 --> 00:16:13,614
Zeppeli: HE IS A ZOMBIE.

327
00:16:13,680 --> 00:16:16,617
THEY MUST FEED
ON LIVING FLESH TO SURVIVE.

328
00:16:16,683 --> 00:16:20,420
HOWEVER, THEY ARE IN CONSTANT
THRALL TO THEIR MASTER,

329
00:16:20,486 --> 00:16:22,422
NOT UNLIKE MARIONETTES.

330
00:16:22,488 --> 00:16:25,526
Jack: OH, YOU LADS IS BOTH
AS WHITE AS A SHEET.

331
00:16:25,592 --> 00:16:27,694
ALL THE BLOOD IS
DRAINED FROM YOUR FACES.

332
00:16:27,794 --> 00:16:30,697
MAYBE I SHOULD CUT OFF
THOSE USELESS HEADS OF YOURS

333
00:16:30,797 --> 00:16:33,934
AND WATCH IT SPRAY
OUTTA YOUR NECKS.

334
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:35,368
( both gasp )

335
00:16:35,435 --> 00:16:38,204
Jack: NOW,
YOU MEWLING CORPSES‐TO‐BE,

336
00:16:38,304 --> 00:16:40,707
PREPARE FOR THE CARNAGE!

337
00:16:40,807 --> 00:16:43,376
Zeppeli: TELL ME,
WHAT'S HIS NEXT MOVE?

338
00:16:43,443 --> 00:16:45,178
YOU MUST THINK AS HE DOES.

339
00:16:45,211 --> 00:16:48,882
JOJO, THIS STRATEGY
WILL SERVE YOU IN GOOD STEAD.

340
00:16:48,982 --> 00:16:52,318
ASK YOURSELF, "WHAT WOULD BE
THE MOST ADVANTAGEOUS THING

341
00:16:52,385 --> 00:16:54,855
FOR MY FOE TO DO NEXT?"

342
00:16:54,888 --> 00:16:56,356
HIM, FOR EXAMPLE.

343
00:16:56,389 --> 00:16:58,625
IF HE BLOCKS OFF
THE TUNNEL ENTRANCE,

344
00:16:58,692 --> 00:17:01,334
WE CAN'T RETREAT
TO THE SUNLIGHT.

345
00:17:01,401 --> 00:17:05,038
( Jack growls )

346
00:17:05,071 --> 00:17:06,072
( both gasp )

347
00:17:09,075 --> 00:17:12,345
Zeppeli: JUST AS I PREDICTED,
HE'S BLOCKED OUR RETREAT!

348
00:17:12,412 --> 00:17:13,714
JoJo: SPEEDWAGON, JUMP!

349
00:17:21,254 --> 00:17:22,523
Zeppeli: TRY HARDER.

350
00:17:22,589 --> 00:17:24,424
( Jack growling )

351
00:17:26,760 --> 00:17:30,330
( JoJo gasps )
KNIVES ARE COMING OUT OF HIM.

352
00:17:30,396 --> 00:17:31,765
Speedwagon: BARON ZEPPELI,

353
00:17:31,865 --> 00:17:34,200
YOU DIDN'T SAY NOTHING
ABOUT FIGHTING A PINCUSHION.

354
00:17:34,267 --> 00:17:36,202
♪

355
00:17:36,269 --> 00:17:38,605
( Jack roars )

356
00:17:38,672 --> 00:17:40,373
Zeppeli: HAMON CUTTER!

357
00:17:40,440 --> 00:17:41,775
HAH HAH HAH HAH!

358
00:17:43,443 --> 00:17:44,444
Jack: EH?

359
00:17:44,511 --> 00:17:45,879
Zeppeli: I'M AFRAID YOUR BLADES

360
00:17:45,946 --> 00:17:48,414
ARE RATHER DULL
COMPARED TO MY HAMON CUTTER.

361
00:17:48,448 --> 00:17:51,618
JOJO, THIS CREATURE
ILLUSTRATES A PRINCIPLE.

362
00:17:51,718 --> 00:17:53,754
IMAGINE A MINUSCULE FLEA,

363
00:17:53,787 --> 00:17:56,623
SO SMALL THAT IT'S
BARELY VISIBLE.

364
00:17:56,723 --> 00:17:59,760
WHY IS IT THEY BITE HUMANS
WHO TOWER OVER THEM

365
00:17:59,793 --> 00:18:02,035
WITHOUT A SINGLE THOUGHT
TO THEIR OWN SAFETY?

366
00:18:02,102 --> 00:18:04,738
WOULD YOU CALL
THEIR BEHAVIOR COURAGEOUS?

367
00:18:04,805 --> 00:18:07,641
OF COURSE NOT.
IT'S HUNGER COMPELLING THEM.

368
00:18:07,708 --> 00:18:10,076
I WILL TELL YOU
WHAT COURAGE IS, JOJO.

369
00:18:10,143 --> 00:18:12,813
COURAGE IS TO LOOK
YOUR FEAR IN THE EYE

370
00:18:12,913 --> 00:18:15,582
AND KNOW THAT IT HAS
NO DOMINION OVER YOU!

371
00:18:15,649 --> 00:18:17,483
FEAR SCATTERS YOUR BREATHING.

372
00:18:17,551 --> 00:18:19,986
WHEN YOU TOSS YOUR FEAR
INTO THE DUST,

373
00:18:20,086 --> 00:18:22,723
BREATHING IS THE SWORD
EVER AT YOUR HIP.

374
00:18:22,789 --> 00:18:26,159
BREATHE WITH COURAGE, AND YOU
WILL NEVER WANT FOR HAMON.

375
00:18:26,226 --> 00:18:28,228
BRAVERY IS
OUR BIRTHRIGHT, LADS!

376
00:18:28,294 --> 00:18:31,565
AND FOR ALL THE ABILITIES
THEY MAY BRING INTO A BATTLE,

377
00:18:31,632 --> 00:18:33,499
COURAGE IS SOMETHING
A ZOMBIE RELINQUISHED

378
00:18:33,600 --> 00:18:34,668
WHEN HE TOOK THIS FORM!

379
00:18:34,735 --> 00:18:36,570
THEY'RE NO BETTER THAN FLEAS!

380
00:18:36,637 --> 00:18:40,106
SENDO WAVE KICK!

381
00:18:41,341 --> 00:18:42,509
( both gasp )

382
00:18:42,609 --> 00:18:45,278
Zeppeli: A KNEE FULL OF HAMON
TO THE HEAD

383
00:18:45,345 --> 00:18:48,281
SEEMS TO HAVE CURED
THIS ONE'S BRAGGADOCIO.

384
00:18:48,348 --> 00:18:51,618
Speedwagon: I DON'T BELIEVE IT.
HE DIDN'T EVEN SPILL ANY WINE.

385
00:18:51,685 --> 00:18:53,954
Zeppeli: JOJO,
YOU FINISH THE CREATURE OFF.

386
00:18:54,020 --> 00:18:56,456
DESTROY THE BRAIN.
IT'S THE ONLY WAY.

387
00:18:56,523 --> 00:18:59,459
ANYTHING ELSE,
AND YOU RISK IT COMING BACK.

388
00:19:01,535 --> 00:19:03,704
( Jack roars )

389
00:19:04,605 --> 00:19:05,772
TIME FOR THE SLAUGHTER,

390
00:19:05,839 --> 00:19:08,975
NAUGHTY LITTLE PIGS.

391
00:19:09,042 --> 00:19:11,477
( wall rumbles )

392
00:19:11,545 --> 00:19:14,648
I'LL CUT YOU TO SHREDS
ONE BY ONE.

393
00:19:14,715 --> 00:19:15,949
Speedwagon: DON'T TELL ME

394
00:19:16,016 --> 00:19:17,618
WE'RE FOLLOWING HIM
INTO THAT PASSAGEWAY.

395
00:19:17,684 --> 00:19:19,052
Zeppeli: IT HAS TO BE DESTROYED,

396
00:19:19,119 --> 00:19:21,855
BUT WE WILL BE DOING
NO SUCH THING.

397
00:19:21,888 --> 00:19:23,690
‐ JOJO...
‐ ( JoJo gasps )

398
00:19:23,724 --> 00:19:26,693
Zeppeli: I EXPECT YOU
TO FINISH OFF THIS ABOMINATION

399
00:19:26,727 --> 00:19:28,562
WITHOUT SPILLING A SINGLE DROP.

400
00:19:28,629 --> 00:19:31,865
ALL RIGHT, ONE LAST BIT
OF ADVICE BEFORE YOU GO.

401
00:19:31,898 --> 00:19:34,901
THERE WERE NO VIKINGS
IN THE LAND OF NORWAY

402
00:19:34,968 --> 00:19:38,071
UNTIL THE NORTH WIND
BLEW IN AND CREATED THEM.

403
00:19:38,171 --> 00:19:41,374
IF EVEN ONE DROP OF THAT VINO
GOES TO WASTE,

404
00:19:41,407 --> 00:19:44,645
I DON'T CARE HOW UTTERLY
YOU DEFEAT THE ZOMBIE.

405
00:19:44,711 --> 00:19:46,913
I WILL ABANDON YOU HERE AND NOW.

406
00:19:46,980 --> 00:19:49,482
‐ ( JoJo gasps )
‐ Speedwagon: OI!

407
00:19:49,550 --> 00:19:51,652
LISTEN TO YOURSELF.
HAVE YOU GONE INSANE?

408
00:19:51,718 --> 00:19:53,754
Zeppeli: I KNOW WHAT I'M DOING!

409
00:19:54,655 --> 00:19:56,089
I WILL DO MY BEST.

410
00:19:56,189 --> 00:19:59,259
LIKE THE VIKINGS, I WILL BE
STRENGTHENED BY HARDSHIP.

411
00:19:59,359 --> 00:20:00,534
( Speedwagon gasps )

412
00:20:00,601 --> 00:20:02,202
( Zeppeli grunts )

413
00:20:03,303 --> 00:20:04,370
JoJo: IT'S A LABYRINTH.

414
00:20:04,437 --> 00:20:05,772
EVEN WITH THIS TORCH,

415
00:20:05,839 --> 00:20:08,208
ALL IT'S DOING IS
CASTING SHADOWS TO BEDEVIL ME.

416
00:20:08,308 --> 00:20:11,144
( footsteps echoing )

417
00:20:11,211 --> 00:20:12,513
( gasps ) THE TORCH!

418
00:20:12,546 --> 00:20:14,214
I'M BRIGHT AS DAY TO HIM!

419
00:20:17,483 --> 00:20:19,052
( yells )

420
00:20:19,119 --> 00:20:20,353
( gasps )

421
00:20:20,386 --> 00:20:22,155
( Jack laughs )

422
00:20:22,222 --> 00:20:25,826
JoJo: ALL THIS DOES
IS ILLUMINATE MY POSITION,

423
00:20:25,892 --> 00:20:28,795
BUT WITHOUT IT, I HAVEN'T
A CLUE WHERE HE'S LURKING

424
00:20:28,862 --> 00:20:30,564
OR FROM WHERE HE'LL STRIKE.

425
00:20:36,970 --> 00:20:40,907
Jack: EVEN IN THE DARK, I CAN
SMELL THE BLOOD FROM HIS ARM.

426
00:20:40,974 --> 00:20:45,245
JoJo: I MUST THINK LIKE MY FOE,
JUST AS THE BARON COMMANDED.

427
00:20:45,345 --> 00:20:47,080
I'M SURE HE'S CLOSE.

428
00:20:47,180 --> 00:20:50,517
NEXT, I MUST MASTER MY FEAR,
LEST IT SAP MY HAMON.

429
00:20:50,584 --> 00:20:52,553
BREATHING IS
THE SWORD AT MY HIP.

430
00:20:52,586 --> 00:20:55,255
Jack: THAT'S IT.
A LITTLE CLOSER,

431
00:20:55,355 --> 00:20:58,324
AND I'LL BE PICKING MY TEETH
WITH YOUR BONES, BOY.

432
00:20:58,391 --> 00:21:02,235
Zeppeli: THE HARSH WIND BLOWING
DOWN OFF OF THE ARCTIC OCEAN

433
00:21:02,268 --> 00:21:03,904
BIRTHED THE FEARSOME VIKINGS.

434
00:21:03,937 --> 00:21:07,407
ONLY WHEN WE ARE TOSSED HEADLONG
INTO THE CRUCIBLE OF ADVERSITY

435
00:21:07,440 --> 00:21:09,075
DO WE RISE TO THE CHALLENGE.

436
00:21:09,109 --> 00:21:11,912
WHAT WILL A GLASS OF VINO
CREATE THIS NIGHT?

437
00:21:11,945 --> 00:21:16,449
IF HE SHOULD FAIL,
DIO HAS ALREADY WON.

438
00:21:16,550 --> 00:21:18,885
JoJo: WHAT?
THE WINE IS RIPPLING.

439
00:21:18,952 --> 00:21:22,523
OF COURSE. JUST LIKE WHEN WE
WERE TRAINING IN THE STREAM.

440
00:21:22,589 --> 00:21:24,791
IT'S CONDUCTING THE HAMON.

441
00:21:24,891 --> 00:21:27,293
IT PASSES
THROUGH THE GLASS, MY ARM,

442
00:21:27,360 --> 00:21:29,730
MY BODY, THE GROUND ITSELF!

443
00:21:29,796 --> 00:21:32,866
I CAN FEEL HIS VIBRATIONS
IN THE WINE.

444
00:21:32,933 --> 00:21:36,537
WITH HAMON,
ALL IS MADE CLEAR TO ME NOW.

445
00:21:36,603 --> 00:21:38,304
MY SPIRIT TREMBLES!

446
00:21:38,404 --> 00:21:40,306
MY HEART IS ABLAZE!

447
00:21:40,406 --> 00:21:41,642
I'VE FOUND YOU, ZOMBIE!

448
00:21:41,708 --> 00:21:44,645
THESE STONES
OFFER NO PROTECTION!

449
00:21:44,711 --> 00:21:47,814
SENDO HAMON OVERDRIVE!

450
00:21:47,914 --> 00:21:50,984
Jack: TURN THE CORNER
SO I CAN FEAST ON YOU.

451
00:21:54,254 --> 00:21:56,790
( screams )

452
00:21:56,823 --> 00:21:58,725
Zeppeli: SOUNDS LIKE
YOU PASSED THE TEST

453
00:21:58,792 --> 00:22:01,167
WITH FLYING COLORS, JOJO.
EXCELLENT.

454
00:22:01,234 --> 00:22:04,137
ADVERSITY HAS
MADE THE LAD A VIKING.

455
00:22:04,170 --> 00:22:05,138
( JoJo exhales )

456
00:22:05,171 --> 00:22:07,140
♪

457
00:22:22,455 --> 00:22:25,792
♪ I'LL BE THE ROUNDABOUT

458
00:22:25,859 --> 00:22:29,630
♪ THE WORDS
WILL MAKE YOU OUT AND OUT ♪

459
00:22:29,696 --> 00:22:34,935
♪ I SPEND THE DAY YOUR WAY

460
00:22:35,001 --> 00:22:37,437
♪ CALL IT MORNING
DRIVING THROUGH THE SOUND ♪

461
00:22:37,504 --> 00:22:42,342
♪ AND IN AND OUT THE VALLEY

462
00:22:49,550 --> 00:22:52,886
